# HERE Maps API for JavaScript browser key (map rendering only).
#
# This must be a SEPARATE, restricted HERE key - never reuse the backend
# HERE_API_KEY here. Browser keys ship in the JS bundle and are visible to
# anyone, so create a dedicated key in the HERE platform and restrict it
# (e.g. to your app's domains and to the Maps API for JavaScript).
#
# Copy this file to web/.env and fill in the key. NEVER commit web/.env.
VITE_HERE_MAPS_API_KEY=
